    <updated>2025-06-04T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <id>https://otsuka.haus/reviews/2025-06-04-a-complete-unknown/</id>
    <content type="html">&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;if i was rating timothée chalamet, edward norton, and monica barbaro for their performances, this would be ★★★★★&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;bob dylan is self-absorbed, johnny cash likes him for it?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;maybe stop introducing new musicians every 2 scenes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;honestly not sure what more there is to this movie besides being a vehicle to let timmy tim perform dylan songs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</content>
